narrative.title: Provider Overview
narrative.text: Florida Clinical Practice Association INC is a Surgery provider based in Gainesville, FL. From the 2018–2024 period, this provider received $79.3M in Medicaid payments across 5.6M claims.

narrative.title: Why This Matters
narrative.text: At $79.3M in Medicaid payments, this provider represents significant public healthcare spending. Understanding where these dollars go helps ensure the program serves those who need it most.
